		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I enjoyed it. The final boss was pretty difficult. I'm not all that great a gamer so I'm not sure how the rest of you fared, but I know it took me many tries, beating all 8 bosses and finally arriving at Wily with enough energy tanks to beat his final form. The first form is ridiculously easy, I found I could beat it without losing any energy.
<br />
<br />For me, while the sound track was decent, it didn't have the incisive awesomeness that the 1-6's soundtracks had, or Mega Man X 1-3.

		

